# System Options
# https://forum.snapcraft.io/t/setting-system-options/87

# snap system-wide options operation by 'set' and 'get' commands
snap get system some.option
snap set system some.option="SomeValue"
snap unset system some.option
snap set system some.option! # from snapd v2.41+

# Outputs a top-level view of system-wide option categories
# which can be added as arguments to view their contents
snap get system
snap get system -d # output in JSON format

